    <item>
      <title>中东局势紧张 普京安全委员会主席访问伊朗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/putin-s-security-council-chief-visits-iran-amid-mideast-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在伊朗伊斯兰共和国可能因哈马斯领导人之死对以色列发动报复性袭击的紧张局势加剧之际，俄罗斯安全委员会秘书谢尔盖·绍伊古访问了伊朗，与伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安和高级官员举行会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/putin-s-security-council-chief-visits-iran-amid-mideast-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 11:55:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国总理哈西娜逃亡至伦敦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/bangladesh-s-hasina-headed-to-london-after-fleeing-country</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，谢赫·哈西娜在数千名抗议者的压力下于周一辞去孟加拉国总理一职，预计将前往伦敦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/bangladesh-s-hasina-headed-to-london-after-fleeing-country</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 11:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国称马斯克的“内战不可避免”言论毫无道理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/uk-says-musk-s-civil-war-is-inevitable-post-is-unjustified</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周一，三名女孩被杀，有关凶手的错误信息四处传播，引发了为期一周的骚乱，英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的政府对亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的言论进行了猛烈抨击，马斯克声称英国正走向内战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/uk-says-musk-s-civil-war-is-inevitable-post-is-unjustified</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 11:41:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠誉将肯尼亚债券评级进一步下调至垃圾级，导致其债券价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/kenya-bonds-fall-as-fitch-cuts-credit-rating-deeper-into-junk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级因预算风险将肯尼亚信用评级进一步下调至垃圾级，随后该国美元债券价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/kenya-bonds-fall-as-fitch-cuts-credit-rating-deeper-into-junk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 11:03:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
